node.text: My art traits :D✨ there was a couple more like the unblended blush lines and shiny hair that I didn’t add but here’s what I was able to fit in! 💗#digitalart

SHOP REOPENING!!! 💗🌟🍈
My print shop is re-opening on the 31st In celebration of my birthday being the same day 😭 so only a few days away! new products such as sticky notes, mouse pads and note pads have been added as well as new prints and the return of some sold out items! I’ll be extending shipping to the US, Canada, the UK and Australia 💗🌟

node.text: A tribute piece to me, and my childhood dog who recently passed. I miss him dearly and I wish time didn’t go by so fast, but I want to celebrate the times I had with him and my relationship with him. Rocco was the perfect dog for my soul and the perfect dog for my family, I’ll never forget the love and laughter he brought to my life, he watched me grow up into the woman I am today, he was truly the coolest little guy. Rest easy boy, I love you rocco! ♥️
